metadata.name: PsyKidd Reborn
metadata.description:
Created using my original 'PsyKidd' piece as a reference, rebirthing an old piece with my improved style and skill



I created my first PsyKidd piece when I first got out of jail and needed to make changes to my life and felt it was useless due to how people, jobs and even family see and treat you after you've been in jail
